{"tid":789261,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"阿嬌自爆入娛樂圈只為養家 倘時間重來不會當明星","createTime":"2018-08-22T06:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-22T10:09:36.000Z","uid":76329,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d64ed3cd35740491d6bd4a63508b8c7b001daf","tid":789261,"uid":76329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"鍾欣潼（阿嬌）近日在內地訪談節目《舉杯呵呵喝》中提及自己的演藝事業，她坦言自己不擅言辭，並不適合演藝圈，當初選擇進入演藝圈全是為了養家。<br />\n<br />\n出道18年的阿嬌在節目中難得吐露真性情，指自己性格不適合在演藝圈發展，亦從沒想過要當明星，「其實，我做這個職業是因為要養家，希望我家人可以過得好。」她透露，自己出生在單親家庭，沒有與同齡人一樣的正常童年，由幼兒園到小學已經轉學7次，因此不懂得如何與人交流、溝通。<br />\n<br />\n阿嬌又指，如果時光真的可以重來，想回到20年前，放棄現在的一切，也不會再當明星，去尋找自己遺失的童年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 時光倒流，我唔會再同希哥影相，唔比佢做漢堡神偷"},{"pid":"158e1caecf740bb9d5e02264dae2843c3536016d","tid":789261,"uid":177734,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T07:44:11.000Z","msg":"個個都要養家，唔通個個都想養家咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552793f6b44bd7c41f2a1ca7619222f28722b9e8","tid":789261,"uid":185126,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:26:56.000Z","msg":"賣鮑養家<br />\n孝感動天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2094d5aa1cab34e571ff505f5766fa4417417b00","tid":789261,"uid":41343,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:27:03.000Z","msg":"阿嬌又指，如果時光真的可以重來，想回到20年前，放棄現在的一切，也不會再當明星，去尋找自己遺失的童年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n19歲出道關童年咩事"},{"pid":"5db57f5830243c9f33d3866d8f21e60c4f1890af","tid":789261,"uid":66,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"佢好似到依家仲要養埋佢個同母異父嘅妹<br />\n仲要供書教學<br />\n淫照個排勁唔掂都要出返黎撈<br />\n就係因為要養佢地成家<br />\n覺得佢係on9版張柏芝<br />\n成家人都當佢係搖錢樹咁"},{"pid":"bcc3e6ba6dd1b2e77edeff53a386518bc6e8a2f6","tid":789261,"uid":65128,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:42:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9634d2a7479297295e3d3c7e38488c9bc167181d","tid":789261,"uid":31841,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"佢同阿希扑野冇收錢喎，點養家"},{"pid":"58b82ca5398be66f1dec3520272eebeae5a69027","tid":789261,"uid":60281,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:43:45.000Z","msg":"唔係閃卡事件佢會唔會咁講？<br />\n發生之前Twins紅到癲"},{"pid":"b4e11015727a7a3c1d2c60b5269b14d86827d1e9","tid":789261,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T09:49:45.000Z","msg":"唔識同人相處 肯定仲係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a6e9f617beeab79fb5642bdfbabbce07e6d0d00","tid":789261,"uid":168172,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:01:15.000Z","msg":"唔識做人姐"},{"pid":"89a5637d2354be9da925af54921c321d05edd4c7","tid":789261,"uid":40499,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:03:59.000Z","msg":"呀嬌呀嬌係反皮的"},{"pid":"d3c9fb76dead241530f7f78bcc4ac368301ce394","tid":789261,"uid":84633,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"不擅言辭又真係<br />\n<br />\n你睇阿sa同佢分別幾大<br />\n<br />\n寫同講都係"}]}